        "setup ENG": "\"Holy crap.\" The fuel tanker sits just off the road, and it appears in excellent condition. You exit your car, and checking the perimeter you approach the cab, it's driver side door hanging open. You slice the seat belt apart, and bludgeon the head of the zombie that falls out. The trucker's bloody hat says Beaver Inspector, and you marvel al how stupid and frivolous your species used to be. Climbing into the cab you give the keys a twist and the loud diesel engine roars to life like some ancient monster reborn into the world. You cringe. Noise like that is going to draw every dead thing for a mile.",
