        "setup ENG": "\"Don't pretend I'm the only one who's thought about this. We all have. I've seen it in your faces. These people use up all our resources, but contribute nothing. I'm not trying to be cruel - just survive.\"\r\nI can't believe you're even talking about this. You know it would be murder to leave these people to the dead. Is survival worth sacrificing our own humanity? Are we no better than the monsters we hide from? Every player with 1 or more survivors at the colony must vole with a thumbs up or down. The option with the most votes takes effect.",
