        "setup ENG": "The snow falls heavily as the world turns white and visibility drops to only a few yards around you. Of course a blizzard would come now. You're not alone though. Another shape moves through the storm, gesticulating wildly as it struggles through the snow. And the another. And still another. Your stomach lurches as you realize you've walked into the middle of a roving horde of the dead. Weighing your options you suspect the reduced visibility may help you pass with minimum detection. But you also have to admit the odds are not in your favor.",
