        "No.": 38,
        "Title ENG": "Sewer Passage",
        "Title SRB": "Kanalizacioni prolaz",
        "Condition ENG": "If a survivor the player controls is at the library:",
        "Condition SRB": "Ako se preživeli koga kontroliše igrač nalazi u biblioteci:",
        "setup ENG": "You casually walk past an aisle or public records, when an idea strikes you. In half an hour you locate the city's sewage layout, and plot a route that goes from a manhole just outside the colony all the way to the hospital. You show your findings to the colony but no one is interested in traversing a pitch black labyrinth of waste.",
        "Set-up SRB": "Dok ležerno hodaš pored prolaza javne evidencije padne ti na pamet jedna ideja. U roku od pola sata pronalaziš plan kanalizacije i upisuješ rutu kojom treba da se krećeš da bi stigao od šahte koja se nalazi pored kolonije do bolnice. Pokazuješ svoju ideju u koloniji ali niko nije zainteresovan za mrkli mrak u lavirintu otpada.",
        "Option 1 /Thumbs Up ENG:": "You're terrified but know this is your chance to do something meaningful for the colony, even if they don't realize it. You decide to try to clear a path. Choose a survivor you control at the library. Roll a die. Roll for exposure on the chosen survivor a number of times equal to the die result. If you are not killed by those exposure rolls, survivors do not have to roll for exposure for the remainder of the game, when moving from the colony to the hospital or from the hospital to the colony. Place this card next to the hospital as a reference.",
        "Option 1 SRB:": "Preplašeni ste ali znate da je ovo vaša šansa da uradite nešto bitno za koloniju bez obzira što to niko ne razume. Odlučio si da probaš da pročistiš put. Izaberi preživelog koga kontrolišeš u biblioteci. Baci D6 kockicu, bacaš za \"exposure\" za izabranog preživelog onoliko puta koliko je bilo na D6 kockici. Ako preživeli nije poginuo, svi preživeli ne moraju da bacaju za \"exposure\" do kraja igre kada se kreću od kolonije do bolnice i obratno. Postavite ovu karticu pored bolnice kao podsetnik.",
        "Option 2 /Thumbs Down ENG:": "Nothing happens.",
