        "Title ENG": "Spoiled",
        "Title SRB": "Razmaženost",
        "Condition ENG": "If the player spends a food, after removing food from the supply but before increasing the action die result:",
        "Condition SRB": "Ako igrač potroši hranu iz ostave a pre nego za 1 poveća rezultat jedne \"action\" kockice:",
        "setup ENG": "You stare at the can of stew, desperately hoping you're not seeing what you think you see. Is the can bulging or is it just misshapen from being dropped? You're not in a rush to het botulism, but food isn't exactly plentiful around here",
        "Set-up SRB": "Zagledan u konzervu gulaša, očajnicki se nadaš da je ono što vidiš stvarno. Da li je konzerva zaobljena ili je to samo deformacija zato što je pala na pod. Nisi u žurbi da se boriš sa trovanjem i groznicom ali hrane baš i nemaš u izobilju.",
        "Option 1 /Thumbs Up ENG:": "You shake your head. \"I'm sure it's fine. I've got to stop being so paranoid.\" Choose a survivor you control and place a wound on it. Proceed to increase the action die result.",
        "Option 1 SRB:": "Vrtiš glavom. \"Siguran sam da je dobra. Moram da prestanem da budem paranoičan.\" Izaberi preživelog koga kontrolišeš i stavi jednu ranu na njega. Povećaj vrednost \"action\" kockice za 1 kako si planirao.",
        "Option 2 /Thumbs Down ENG:": "Better to lose a few pounds from hunger than lose everything to illness. You throw the can away. You do not increase your action die result. The food is still spent.",
        "Option 2 SRB": "Bolje izgubiti nekoliko kilograma zbog gladi nego izgubiti sve zbog bolesti. Bacaš konzervu daleko. Ne povećavaš \"action\" kockicu za 1."
