        "Option 1 /Thumbs Up ENG:": "\"Great idea as always Harold.\" You open the gates for the old man and his wife. Remove 2 helpless survivor tokens in the colony from the game. The very next morning they're found at the gates, staring in hungrily at the living. Lose 1 morale.",
