        "Option 1 /Thumbs Up ENG:": "\"I understand better than you think. Perhaps I knew this day was coming. But your happiness is more important to me than anything, so I won't stand in your way.\" Remove a survivor card from your following and add it to the following of a player that has fewer survivors than you.",
