        "Option 1 /Thumbs Up ENG:": "You dive for the gun and take aim. You struggle to pull the trigger, but soon he's right on top of you, his hands scrabbling at your feet \"I'm sorry Poppa.\" Roll once for exposure on the moved survivor. If the survivor isn't killed attach this card to it. Once per round when this survivor performs an attack do not roll for exposure.",
