        "setup ENG": "Oh thank God you're alive,\" the stranger says. \"I was afraid you were one of the dead ones. God, I'm in a bad shape. I was with some others I met a few weeks ago but our group was gradually split up or killed. It'd sure be great to team up with somebody again. You got a group?\" Your gaze wanders from the stranger's eyes to the blood-soaked rags wrapped around their right hand. \"Oh this? This is nothing man. Just cut it up on some broken glass when I was looting a store back there.\" The stranger laughs it off as nothing but they seem nervous about something.",
