        "setup ENG": "There it is again - the sound of a baby crying. You enter the warehouse's back hallway, following the sound, and come to the large trash bin that holds used plastic containers. Someone has thrown away a newborn. A quick investigation yields a distraught teenage girl. Fearing being turned away, she hid her pregnancy from the colony. Every player with 1 or more survivors at the colony must vote with thumbs up or down. The option with the most votes takes effect.",
