        "setup ENG": "Most fortune tellers are grifters, and sure, maybe you kind of are too, but you don't ply your trade by simply predicting things that could apply to anyone. Your mother trained you to be always vigilant and constantly analyzing the world around you. As a result, your brain processes an almost obscene level of detail, allowing you to predict events with surprising accuracy. Not that you'll admit your secret anyone else...",
